data.description: This secluded property has an oversized wrap around vinyl deck to sit and watch the sun sets. Open space behind the property with pasture ground on 1.73 acres. Main floor laundry/mud room with sink/tub off the oversized 2 car attached garage. Hardwood floors in the kitchen and dine-in area. Wonderful open kitchen with stove in the island and all the appliances. An extra formal dining area attached to the living room that features a gas fireplace. Spiral staircase leads you to the upstairs where the primary bedroom features a 5 piece bath. Open storage space in the basement with a walk out. You will not want to miss this beautifully landscaped acreage property with pastures and a 4 stall horse barn. NO Metro district.So many features that can be missed. 2 hydrants in the barn area. One behind the pine tree and 1 next to the barn. Extra shed in the pasture area. A variety of trees including apple trees. 220 electrical in the barn with a tack room. Pump in the basement is for extra pressure for the irrigation system for the lawn. That pump was recently replaced. Fences area around the house is vinyl fence. Notice to the buyer, at the time of the transfer of deed the new buyer will be required to become a part of the HOA.
